name: UITextContentType
desc: Constants that identify the semantic meaning for a text-entry area.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Creates a text content type with the specified raw value.

items.name: static let URL: UITextContentType
items.desc: A property that defines the content in a text input area as a URL.

items.name: static let namePrefix: UITextContentType
items.desc: A property that defines the content in a text input area as a prefix or title, such as Dr.

items.desc: A property that defines the content in a text input area as a family name, or last name.

items.name: static let nickname: UITextContentType
items.desc: A property that defines the content in a text input area as a nickname.
